For the Scottish boxer (born 1925), see Skeets Gallacher.Richard "Skeets" Gallagher (July 28, 1891 - May 22, 1955) was an American actor. He had blue eyes and his naturally blond hair was tinged with grey from the age of sixteen. For the_American_basketball_coach , see Richard_F._Gallagher .
